item.title: Why is their only one server that the ipban works on?
item.dc:creator: @jungledude jungledude
item.description:
@jungledude wrote:

What your problem is is that you server dose not save a new char file then read it. It reads it and dose not find it and saves a new one and just goes. You need to make it read the char file before logging the person in. Or you can do what I do search “moreinfo file not found” or char file or w/e (normally both) and then in that code after it says it was not found add disconnected = true; it is very simple
